# Frontend Ownership

**Owner:** frontend (UI/App).

These paths are owned by frontend: `web/**`, `app/**`, `components/**`, `ui/**`. Other workers must not edit these directly; use `/handoff` to request changes from frontend.

When working in this area: pages, components, state, client validation, UX flows, error UI. Use skills: ui-patterns, test-playbook (frontend tests), api-patterns (when syncing contract).
